snippet.title: RADtv - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
RADtv is a hot-seat multiplayer VR game for Oculus Rift coming to Steam and Oculus store on August 2nd, 2019! Get sucked into the channels of a sentient TV and compete in quick-fire games to be crowned RADtv champion.

Wishlist RADtv on steam:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/649240/RADtv/

Join us for more RAD times: 

Twitter: https://twitter.com/ruffiangames
Discord: https://discord.gg/Wz26pdc
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/RuffianGames/
